getCurrentlyAdoptedTraits

java.util.Set<ITrait> getCurrentlyAdoptedTraits()
Use this to get the list of current ITraits an agent has adopted. Since ITraits count their own frequency, in toto and by tag, this can be useful for certain kinds of frequency-dependent adoption.
